</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="288" pageNumber="289" type="note">
<paragraph pageId="288" pageNumber="289">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="288" pageNumber="289">Whitehead (1972: 201) stated that he was uncertain if the two Central American specimens he saw were conclusively conspecific with those from Florida.</paragraph>
